The exclusive Trunk Show by Abbyke Domina hosted on Sunday, 26 August, at The Polo Avenue, Victoria Island was filled with fun moments. It was an evening of style and relaxation as guests mingled and shopped in style. Guests at the event included Mercy Aigbe, Sina Peller, Jane Michael, Efe Tommy, Bimbo Thomas, Mide Martins, Bambam, Pretty Mike, Tonye Garrick, Olar Slim, amongst others. The women’s ready to wear fashion house, Abbyke Domina, was celebrating 5 years of tremendous growth on Sunday by launching their new colourful and flirty collection, “Tres Chic”. The collection was vibrant and sophisticated, pieces that could be styled to wear anywhere. Here is a glimpse of the exciting event.